Interface KeyValueSystem

  • All Known Implementing Classes:

      • mergeStore

        void mergeStore(alluxio.AlluxioURI fromUri,
                alluxio.AlluxioURI toUri)
         throws IOException,
                alluxio.exception.AlluxioException
        Merges one completed key-value store to another completed key-value store. If there are the same keys from both stores, they are merged too, for these keys, whose value will be retrieved is undetermined.
        Parameters:
        fromUri - the AlluxioURI to the store to be merged
        toUri - the AlluxioURI to the store to be merged to
        Throws:
        IOException - if non-Alluxio error occurs
        alluxio.exception.AlluxioException - if other Alluxio error occurs
